data.description: VERY MOTIVATED SELLER!! Check out this solid built ranch home with stunning stone chimney. Set on a quiet street and conveniently located between Chesterton and Portage with city sewer. Just steps away from Prairie Duneland Bike/Walking Trail and Imagination Park, you'll love all this area has to offer. Spacious backyard comes complete with storage shed and full wood privacy fencing. Inside offers solid hardwood floors, beautifully painted fireplace, newer kitchen floors and stainless kitchen appliances. Daylight basement has roughed in plumbing, new well tank and separate den. Oversized 2.5 car garage can be the perfect work space.  Just minutes away from the Indiana Toll Road, I-94 and the Ogden Dunes Train Station and is part of the Award Winning Duneland School System.
